<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your Fix Check is ready</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#FAF7F2; color:#1F1B16; font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#FAF7F2; padding:24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:560px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #E7E0D6; border-radius:8px; padding:32px 32px 28px;">
          <tr>
            <td>
              <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#B45309; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase;">LaunchLook · Fix Check</p>
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 18px; font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; font-size:24px; line-height:1.25; color:#1F1B16; font-weight:500;">
                Your re-scan is ready, {{ first_name }}.
              </h1>

              <p style="margin:0 0 14px; color:#1F1B16;">
                Here's what changed on <strong>{{ app_name }}</strong> since your last report. The full diff is in the attached PDF.
              </p>

              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 18px; font-size:14px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:8px 12px; background:#F0FDF4; border:1px solid #BBF7D0; border-radius:4px; width:33%; vertical-align:top;">
                    <strong style="color:#15803D;">Fixed</strong><br />{{ fixed_count }}
                  </td>
                  <td style="width:8px;"></td>
                  <td style="padding:8px 12px; background:#FFF7ED; border:1px solid #FED7AA; border-radius:4px; width:33%; vertical-align:top;">
                    <strong style="color:#C2410C;">Still open</strong><br />{{ still_count }}
                  </td>
                  <td style="width:8px;"></td>
                  <td style="padding:8px 12px; background:#F4EFE7; border:1px solid #E7E0D6; border-radius:4px; width:33%; vertical-align:top;">
                    <strong style="color:#B45309;">New</strong><br />{{ new_count }}
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0 0 8px; font-weight:600; color:#1F1B16;">
                {{ verdict.emoji }} {{ verdict.label }}
              </p>
              {% if verdict.summary %}
              <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#6B6359;">{{ verdict.summary }}</p>
              {% endif %}

              {% if fixed %}
              <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-weight:600; font-size:13px; color:#15803D;">What's now fixed</p>
              <ul style="margin:0 0 14px; padding-left:18px; color:#1F1B16; font-size:14px;">
                {% for f in fixed %}
                <li style="margin-bottom:4px;">{{ f.original_title }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
              {% endif %}

              {% if still_present %}
              <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-weight:600; font-size:13px; color:#C2410C;">Still showing up</p>
              <ul style="margin:0 0 14px; padding-left:18px; color:#1F1B16; font-size:14px;">
                {% for s in still_present %}
                <li style="margin-bottom:4px;">{{ s.original_title }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
              {% endif %}

              {% if new %}
              <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-weight:600; font-size:13px; color:#B45309;">New since last scan</p>
              <ul style="margin:0 0 14px; padding-left:18px; color:#1F1B16; font-size:14px;">
                {% for n in new %}
                <li style="margin-bottom:4px;">{{ n.title }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
              {% endif %}

              <p style="margin:0 0 18px; font-size:14px; color:#6B6359;">
                If you fixed something we still flagged, reply with what you changed — sometimes the live site needs a hard refresh or a republish.
              </p>

              <div style="border-top:1px solid #E7E0D6; border-left:3px solid #B45309; padding:14px 16px; margin-top:8px; background:#F4EFE7; border-radius:4px;">
                <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#1F1B16;">
                  Need another pass after the next round? Reply <strong>recheck</strong> ($19, or $9 within 14 days of your original report).
                </p>
              </div>

              <hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #E7E0D6; margin:24px 0 16px;" />
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#6B6359;">
                LaunchLook · <a href="https://launchlook.app" style="color:#B45309; text-decoration:none;">launchlook.app</a> · prepared {{ delivered_at }}
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
